Delicious! We made this as a creme brulee. Be sure to strain the custard before pouring it into the cups; that will keep the texture smooth. Also, we recommend dulce de leche instead of caramel for a richer flavor

Rating: 4
A delicious flan recipe; we enjoyed this as a creme brulee. After mixing ingredients, strain before pouring into cups for smoother texture, and use a spoon to spoon off any bubbles on the surface. Used dulce de leche instead of caramel sauce -- I recommend this for more authentic flavor.